[Name] LibXv
[Summary] X11 Video extension library
[Description] LibXv provides an X Window System client interface to the
XVideo extension to the X protocol. 

The XVideo extension allows for accelerated drawing of videos. Hardware
adaptors are exposed to clients, which may draw in a number of colourspaces,
including YUV.
[License] Other
[Homepage] http://www.x.org
